Definition: medium to large tree of tropical North and South America having odd-pinnate leaves and long panicles of small pale yellow flowers followed by scarlet fruits
Synonyms: bitterwood, Simarouba_glauca, bitterwood_tree, genus_Simarouba, m, medium, to, large, tree, of, tropical, North, and, South, America, having, odd-pinnate, leaves, long, panicles, small, pale, yellow, flowers, followed, by, scarlet, fruits
Category: noun.plant
